OL,3,CThousands targeted by fraudsters
OL,4,Cimpersonating financial regulator
OL,6,FConsumers are being targeted by
OL,7,Ffraudsters impersonating the Financial
OL,8,FConduct Authority, the regulator
OL,9,Fwarned, after receiving thousands of
OL,10,Ffake scam reports.
OL,12,FThe watchdog said it received 4,465
OL,13,Freports of scammers pretending to be
OL,14,Fthe FCA in the first half of the year.
OL,16,FThe fraudsters seek to steal money by
OL,17,Fgetting people to hand over funds or
OL,18,Fsensitive information, such as bank
OL,19,Faccount PINs and passwords.
