OL,3,CThousands targeted by fraudsters
OL,4,Cimpersonating financial regulator
OL,6,FAround 480 victims were duped into
OL,7,Fsending money to the fraudsters over
OL,8,Fthe half-year, the FCA said.
OL,10,FIt said the majority, almost two-
OL,11,Fthirds, of reports came from people
OL,12,Faged 56 or above.
OL,14,FThe FCA said that one of the most scam
OL,15,Fmethods involves fraudsters claiming
OL,16,Fthat the regulator has recovered funds
OL,17,Ffrom a crypto wallet that was opened
OL,18,Fillegally in the individual's name.
