OL,3,CThousands targeted by fraudsters
OL,4,Cimpersonating financial regulator
OL,6,FAnother common method is to target
OL,7,Fvulnerable loan scam victims and claim
OL,8,Fthe FCA can help them recover the
OL,9,Fmoney they have lost.
OL,11,FIt said they are then persuaded to
OL,12,Fhand over further funds to who they
OL,13,Fbelieve is the regulator.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, a separate trend has
OL,16,Finvolved fraudsters emailing consumers
OL,17,Ftelling them their creditors have
OL,18,Ftaken out a County Court Judgment
OL,19,Fagainst them and they need to pay the
OL,20,FFCA the monies owed.
