OL,6,FSteve Smart, joint executive director
OL,7,Fof enforcement and market oversight at
OL,8,Fthe FCA, said: "Fraudsters are
OL,9,Fruthless.
OL,11,F"They attempt to steal money from
OL,12,Finnocent victims by impersonating the
OL,13,FFCA.
OL,15,F"We will never ask you to transfer
OL,16,Fmoney to us or for sensitive banking
OL,17,Finformation such as account PINs and
OL,18,Fpasswords. If in doubt, always check."
